# Contact form delivery (Web3Forms — free, no backend).
# 1. Go to https://web3forms.com → "Create Access Key" using connect@elomagroup.com.au
# 2. Paste the key below, then copy this file to ".env" and restart/rebuild.
# The key is a PUBLIC key (safe to expose in the browser) — that is how Web3Forms works.
VITE_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=
